              "type": "SparqlAskAssertion",
              "query": "ASK { <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/shacl/TransferActShape> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#NodeShape> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#targetClass> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/possessio/TransferAct> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#property> [ <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/possessio/transferQuantity> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#datatype> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#maxCount> 1 ] ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#sparql> [ <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> \"Fungible TransferAct must record exactly one possessio:transferQuantity.\" ], [ <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> \"Non-fungible TransferAct must not carry possessio:transferQuantity.\" ] . }",
              "expectedBoolean": true
            }
          ]
        }
